<b>How to use this song - </b>3/2/01 2:52:53 PM<br>~ <b>Kocho Divah</b><blockquote>Approach the merchant you wish to raise faction with. Make sure a counter or other obstacle is not in the way. Con them, and note your faction (indifferent, etc...) Then whip out your wind instrument (not sure if this helps at all, but can't hurt), target the merchant, and play the song. You will see a message, and then the song will stop. Con them again. You will notice your faction went up one or two rankings. Do your transaction. This faction increase will work with all the same faction-npc's in the zone until you zone, or at least for a long time anyway.<br><br>Not all prices will drop/rise. But it can save you a few plat and gold on some things, so you might as well try if you are thrifty.</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
